Suman Mandanna’s husband’s name is Madan Mandanna, who owns a coffee shop. Suman Mandanna and Madan Mandanna couple do not have any sons, they have only two daughters named Shiman Mandanna & Rashmika Mandanna.

Some Facts About Suman Mandanna

Suman Mandanna is the mother of Indian Tollywood and Bollywood actress Rashmika Mandanna.

Rashmika Mandanna is the elder daughter of Suman Mandanna, her second daughter Shiman Mandanna is much younger. There is a difference of almost 15 years between Shiman Mandanna and Rashmika Mandanna. Rashmika Mandanna is 15 years older than Shiman Mandanna.

Suman Mandanna’s elder daughter Rashmika Mandanna got engaged to Rakshith Shetty in 2018 but after a few days, both of them decided to separate. After their engagement, they both separated before their marriage could take place. Suman Mandanna looked very happy about the engagement of her daughters Rashmika Mandanna and Rakshith Shetty, she also gave an interview.

Suman Mandanna’s daughter Rashmika Mandanna is a very famous actress. She has acted in many superhit films like Animal, Pushpa, Geetha Govindam and Dear Comrade.

Madan Mandanna stays far away from the limelight, she does not even have an account on any social media.

Suman Mandanna is a dog lover.
